# Proteostasis — TODO
=====================================

## Goals & Tasks
-----------------
The Proteostasis project aims to understand the mechanisms of protein stability under temperature fluctuations, develop predictive algorithms, and create an open platform for data sharing. Specific objectives include:
- Establish experimental protocols for thermal stability assays.
- Build a comprehensive database of experimental results.
- Develop and validate machine learning models for stability prediction.
- Publish findings in peer-reviewed journals.
- Organize an international conference on proteostasis.

